Hi,

I am wondering if it is possible to read a parametarized Verilog with Verilator:

> > module or_3(A, B, C, O);
> > parameter WIDTH=2;
> > 
> > input A;
> > input B;
> > input C;
> > output O;
> > wire   C1;
> > 
> > 
> > OR2_X11M_A12TS or_3_stn_or(.Y(C1), .A(A), .B(B));
> > andor_3   or_3_andor(.O(O), .A(C), .B(C), .C(A));
> > 
> > endmodule // test  

It generates an ERROR:

> FAILED TO PROCESS NODE VAR 0x14d4b70 <e150> {e16} w0  WIDTH GPARAM
